Installation:


    make
    cp fbpanel ~/bin             # or somewhere else in your PATH
    mkdir -p ~/.fbpanel          # create config directory
    cp -R config/*  ~/.fbpanel/  # copy sample config files 

Configuration:

   % vi ~/.fbpanel/default        # edit default profile file


Runing

   % fbpanel &                    # same as 'fbpanel -p default &' 

  

